ZH: 这座城市有许多旧建筑。
EN: This city has many old buildings.

ZH: 这是我旧朋友的地址。
EN: This is the address of my old friend.

ZH: 我喜欢收集各种旧邮票。
EN: I like to collect various old stamps.

ZH: 她穿着一件旧外套。
EN: She is wearing an old coat.

ZH: 这家餐馆的装修风格很旧。
EN: The decoration style of this restaurant is very old.

ZH: 我们经常去逛旧书店。
EN: We often go to browse through old bookstores.

ZH: 这台电视机是我家的旧电视机。
EN: This TV set is the old television set in my house.

ZH: 那些旧照片让我想起了很多回忆。
EN: Those old photos bring back a lot of memories.

ZH: 他喜欢收藏旧音乐唱片。
EN: He likes to collect old music records.

ZH: 我捡到了一台旧笔记本电脑。
EN: I found an old laptop.

ZH: 这是我的旧房间，我已经搬出来了。
EN: This is my old room, I have moved out.

ZH: 旧建筑展现出历史的风采。
EN: Old buildings showcase the charm of history.

ZH: 我需要换一部新手机，这部太旧了。
EN: I need to get a new phone, this one is too old.

ZH: 她的妈妈会缝补旧衣服。
EN: Her mother will mend old clothes.

ZH: 我们把旧衣服捐给了慈善机构。
EN: We donated old clothes to a charity organization.

ZH: 这家旧书店有一些罕见的书籍。
EN: This old bookstore has some rare books.

ZH: 我们住在一座旧别墅里。
EN: We live in an old villa.

ZH: 旧照片中的笑容让我感到温暖。
EN: The smiles in the old photos warm my heart.

ZH: 他念旧故里，常怀侨心。
EN: He misses his old hometown, always cherishing his roots.

ZH: 这些旧记录着我们的回忆。
EN: These old records hold our memories.
